      "role": "user",
      "content": "the 1200mg limit is for people just taking it for small aches i think... i've been taking it for a few days now and it's still really bad. if i do the 400mg every 2 hours, i'll definitely be able to make it through the day. is there any real reason why i shouldn't just keep a steady level of it in my system? it seems much more efficient than waiting for the pain to hit again.",
